Full API List (MVP Scope)

Auth
POST /api/auth/register

POST /api/auth/login

GET /api/auth/me

POST /api/auth/logout

User Setup
POST /api/user/linkedin

POST /api/user/resume

GET /api/user/profile

Jobs
POST /api/job/create

GET /api/job/:id

LinkedIn Employee Search
GET /api/linkedin/employees

AI Message Generation
POST /api/message/generate

POST /api/message/bulk-generate

Outreach
POST /api/outreach/send

POST /api/outreach/bulk-send

